Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.05,0:00:05.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:10.66,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to give \Nme an answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:14.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to let you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:18.16,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...that there's somebody \Nhere who's in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:59.54,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, you're stoppin' again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:03.30,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet. I'm going to come back \Nin here with a cool improv riff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It don't mean a thing if \Nyou don't actually play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:08.39,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're havin' \Na good time, Sen-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.48,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I sit in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:11.77,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:13.35,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're early!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:16.26,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I already mentioned \Nthis to Ri-chan's dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:17.85,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,but I've got some good news...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:21.33,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Would you cats be up for playing \Njazz in front of an audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:26.71,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,The bar I worked at here asked us to \Ndo a Christmas performance for 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:31.01,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gaijin bar for U.S. troops stationed \Nhere, so if we're gonna do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:32.74,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,we'd better put some spunk into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:34.84,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Wanna give it a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:35.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:36.02,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.03,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:39.84,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,We got just one month before Christmas, \Nso that doesn't leave us much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.85,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:46.83,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, Sen. Isn't \Nyour birthday on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.05,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm almost 16!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:52.20,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better do a decent performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.53,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, so for starters, \Nlet's try playing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:59.53,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Outta sight! This'll be our first session \Nas a quartet since summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, a one-two-three!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Richie, ain't you gonna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.45,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kaoru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:34.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Once in a while, this guy just freezes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:40.74,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun's got a classical background, \Nso maybe he's shooting for perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:44.50,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you need to do \Nanything complicated at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.74,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,All you really have to do is hit the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.54,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,That's plenty lively for an improvisation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:53.22,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how it felt when \Nyou jumped in and went wild
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.00,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,when we played during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:59.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You said it, Brother Jun! Right on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.89,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Go for broke, Bill Evans!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.64,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he looks like 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:12.10,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Never thought I'd meet Bill \NEvans in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.79,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Now I think we can expect you to play great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:35.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what were you doing \Nthe other day with Yurika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.39,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,In the back of the art room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:41.17,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You saw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:47.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,So are you two already, uh... \Nhaving that kind of relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.30,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What do ya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:52.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell me nothing happened \Nwhen you were dressed like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:57.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a dope! She just asked \Nme to model for her painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:00.65,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,No! Tilt your head more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.70,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Gaze at that twig lovingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:07.16,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get what it was about, \Nbut it was over before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:14.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why am I so relieved?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. That must be it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:27.81,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, she told me to \Nbe her model every week from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. Sounds like there's hope for you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:32.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...if she does something like that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.99,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...! What the hell \Ndo you think you're doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:41.76,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:43.38,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who is that Nishimi guy, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.08,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the "secret boss"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:54.35,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I heard your nephew got the \Ntop score in the final exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:58.17,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful. And he's not just a \Nprodigy, he can play the piano, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:03.55,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well, I don't like how he hasn't \Nbeen getting home 'til late these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.17,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you worry too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:09.00,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's the only male \Nheir in the Nishimi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.98,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make sure he maintains his grades
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.92,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,so he can go to medical school or the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:16.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... Hurry home, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:22.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm surrounded by \Npeople... I'm always alone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.57,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas Sale
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.57,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Furuya Musical Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.57,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Yamaha Pianos, Electones
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:35.46,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, Sen. Isn't \Nyour birthday on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him buying a \Nnew pair for himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:41.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll get them for him, \None jazz musician to another...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:46.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaoru-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:51.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh my gosh! It looks like \Nwe both had the same idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:53.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:56.14,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro is a lucky guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:07:01.31,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know! We'll each buy one stick \Nand give them to him as a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.77,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is a strange development...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:13.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's okay if things stay this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:18.12,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Ri-chan thinks of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.80,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Do you have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:30.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No. Winter in Kyushu is pretty cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be surprised \Nif it started to snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:37.49,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not that cold! It \Nrarely snows here in December.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:38.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:43.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, how did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:48.61,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing! Like in \Na movie! It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.38,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. It melts right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.18,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This won't stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:07.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.52,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:20.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,M-Merry Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:33.43,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, Kota! You're gonna pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.78,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.04,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.44,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you make Ri'ko cry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.42,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's Richie, from when we had watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.05,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what are you doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:49.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing, especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.05,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! He just made Ri'ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What about Ri'ko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:55.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:59.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He's the last person I \Nwanted to see right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:02.24,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, I have to pee...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, how 'bout we all race home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:08.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,The winner gets to have \Nthe biggest piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:10.44,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.17,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Look at 'em go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.49,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna join us for cake too, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:19.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.70,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, your family is rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.57,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bet you have a fancy cake \Nwaitin' for you at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:30.65,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody who takes being surrounded \Nwith a loving family for granted
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:34.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,will never understand that there \Nare people who live in a house
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:37.79,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but have no place in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:43.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Am I jealous of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:50.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Because he has the thing I wish for more\N than anything, but can never have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.30,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Your family's waiting for you, aren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:59.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm around you, it only \Nmakes me feel more miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:25.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Max Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:28.55,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,These are some really nice sticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:32.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank Ri-chan. I just laid \Nout half the money for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:36.39,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so one's from Ri'ko \Nand one's from you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.24,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:41.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:42.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:43.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:44.89,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:51.51,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:52.37,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:57.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:06.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:11.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that kid next to \NRi-chan in all the photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:14.40,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to tell when you see \Nme as a little kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That I got mixed blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:22.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, I'm one of those that ain't \Ngot a place in the house, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.88,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.08,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, America!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:32.04,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you speak English?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:36.80,Main Dialog,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:45.60,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro! Mother! Aren't \NYasuko's things in that box?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.88,Main Dialog,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care, she's no daughter of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:53.11,Main Dialog,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Seducing an enemy soldier, bearing \Nhis child, and in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:57.10,Main Dialog,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,abandoning her shame here \Nbefore running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.09,Main Dialog,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember giving birth \Nto a daughter like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:24.47,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sentaro? Where's Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:35.45,Main Dialog,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,So you didn't see anything either, huh, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:48.28,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, this is apparently a memento
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:52.27,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,your mother left behind when she went away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:56.65,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, the rosary isn't a necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:57.70,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.38,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,You're always wearin' this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.70,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow it a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.93,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:21.49,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's him. Kawabuchi, the \Nkid who went nuts yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:28.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro! You won't have any friends \Nleft if you keep getting into fights!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:32.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:39.80,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,My dad lost his job around then and \Nstayed home gettin' drunk every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:42.26,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't even look me in the eye no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, though, he found \Na job in another prefecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:48.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,said he was gonna live an' \Nwork there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.91,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:56.10,Main Dialog,Sem,0000,0000,0000,,He's still workin' there now, hasn't \Ncome back home in all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:59.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun at home, never a dull moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.83,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,but once in a while, I start thinkin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:06.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...if it's really okay for me to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I said too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm mortified...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:22.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I was so convinced this guy had it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:24.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Those things I yelled at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:57.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're children \Nplaying around on an organ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:18.02,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... What is it, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:23.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's practice some more. Maybe \Neven every day, 'til our gig...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.03,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy! That goes without sayin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.91,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta knock the socks off them Americans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:36.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. This is the guy \Nthat Ri-chan loves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:41.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,My love feels so petty in comparison...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:53.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, we put our all \Ninto every day's session.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:59.86,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Time flew and before we knew \Nit, the day had come...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Our first time on stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:09.12,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:14.31,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Foreign soldiers gather to drink here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:17.91,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It's no place for a young lady like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:21.96,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to listen to jazz. \NI was invited by a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:26.24,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me. You're a respectable customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:28.42,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,After you, young lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:33.08,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me "young lady". \NIt feels like you're mocking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.14,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.96,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko-chan, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.81,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, just play like \Nwe practiced at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.61,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,but feel free to go crazy with \Nit once you get in the groove.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.22,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hang loose and have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:58.24,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, this \Nis the Mukae Tsutomu Quartet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:13.15,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, one-two-three-four...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.63,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He's stiff...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because Yurika-san's watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:45.66,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:17.34,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop! Stop it, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:22.29,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand that coon music jazz!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:26.21,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like a jumble of noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:29.50,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,At least play something white!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's he sayin', Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:36.63,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He says he doesn't like black jazz, \Nso we should play white jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:39.57,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What kinda segregation is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you tryin' to say, old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.43,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Sen-boy! Suck it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:47.44,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get through to a drunk \Nlike that. Just ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:51.02,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. I can't play like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:55.83,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:58.46,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Can you play that one song?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:18:59.89,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,"But Not for Me".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:01.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.98,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the party's \Ngonna end on a sour note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:09.75,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe we can at least \Nlighten up the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:16.08,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It'll just be \Nlike we're playing for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:47.40,Songs,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,They're writing songs of love, but not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:54.21,Songs,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,A lucky star's above, but not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:59.17,Songs,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,With love to lead the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:02.10,Songs,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I've found more clouds of gray
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:07.29,Songs,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,than any Russian play could guarantee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:19.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Jun is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:23.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why Sentaro gets so \Nexcited every time he comes back to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.54,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to admire him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:31.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Brother Jun really surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:34.30,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're the hero of the night, Brother Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:39.51,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Brother Jun, pretending you \Ndon't know what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:42.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! So frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:44.90,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that jerk cuttin' in,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:47.64,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get to play even \Nhalf of what we practiced!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a good experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:52.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The unexpected is really what \Nmakes jazz fun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:55.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to you, soundin' off like an expert!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:57.90,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Am I buggin' you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:00.81,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Um, young la... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:01.57,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.32,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:08.58,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,What shall I call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:14.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Sometimes life is like jazz,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:17.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,and goes in an unexpected direction...
